A representation of the model object 'Modification'. Class for defining bus and branch modifications. It is serialization. However, cross ecore model persistence is not allowed. Reference needs to be broken before serialization, and then re-build after deserialization.

The following features are supported:

  • Any
  • Bus Modify List
  • Branch Modify List
